Package de.parsemis.algorithms.dagminer Description

Contains the DAG Mining Algorithm.

It works on databases containing directed acyclic graphs (DAGs) with arbitrary node labels and a single edge label.

This algorithm bases on a topological node insertion order represented by its canonical form and four extension rules (see the DAGmNewRootExtension, DAGmNewLevelExtension, DAGmNewNodeExtension, and DAGmNewEdgeExtension class).
